title: Multiple Personality Disorder - Surf - Episode 2: The Drive
description: Determined to find waves, The Arnette team winds up on a long and terrible road. Dodging monkey feces they finally find waves deep in the jungle. Chippa Wilson, Fred Patacchia, Ford Archbold, Josh Kerr, Mason Ho and Ezekiel Lau all star.
